{
  "texts": [
    "Key concerns emerge regarding GAI's accuracy in performing mathematical calculations, its occasional reliance on fabricated references, and the presence of conceptual errors within its responses.",
    "While previous examples mostly highlight its limitations, it is important to recognize instances where ChatGPT has been successfully implemented in educational contexts.",
    "The effectiveness of using GAI to foster critical thinking skills within higher education, focusing on its application in introductory chemistry courses, was confirmed by various studies.",
    "In a study by Guo and Lee (2023, pp. 4-6) students engaged in a ChatGPT-based activity involving essay writing, revision, and validation of outputs.",
    "This approach enhanced students' abilities to pose insightful inquiries, analyze information, and understand complex concepts."
  ]
}